NAME
    podusage - Using MooseX::Getopt::Usage and Pod::Usage

SYNOPSIS
        podusage [options]

        --help -? --usage - Bool. Display the usage message and exit
        --man             - Bool. Display man page

OPTIONS
    --help -? --usage
        Display the usage message and exit

    --man
        Display man page

DESCRIPTION
    This program will read the given input file(s) and do something useful
    with the contents thereof.

